 &lt;p&gt;⭐️⭐️⭐️&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/problems/remove-nodes-from-linked-list/description/?envType=daily-question&amp;amp;envId=2024-05-06&#34;&gt;&lt;ins class=&#34;dot&#34;&gt;題目敘述&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are given the  &lt;code&gt;head&lt;/code&gt;  of a linked list.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remove every node which has a node with a greater value anywhere to the right side of it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Return &lt;em&gt;the  &lt;code&gt;head&lt;/code&gt;  of the modified linked list.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-1&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://assets.leetcode.com/uploads/2022/10/02/drawio.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input:&lt;/strong&gt; head = [5,2,13,3,8]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output:&lt;/strong&gt; [13,8]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Explanation:&lt;/strong&gt; The nodes that should be removed are 5, 2 and 3.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Node 13 is to the right of node 5.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Node 13 is to the right of node 2.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Node 8 is to the right of node 3.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input:&lt;/strong&gt; head = [1,1,1,1]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output:&lt;/strong&gt; [1,1,1,1]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Explanation:&lt;/strong&gt; Every node has value 1, so no nodes are removed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;note info no-icon&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ListNode 的 class 內容&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
